Modifications:
- Added by [Ákos Makács]
- Date: 2024-07-14

1. Added PeBusePenaltyLoss and WeightedBusePenaltyLoss to compare hyperbolic feature representation to prototypes.
2. Added Shared2FCHyperbolicBBoxHead that incorporates hyperbolic transformation of the last fully connected layer of the classification branch of the classification head.
3. Added multiple hyperbolic Faster R-CNN configurations using 20, 40, 81, and 100-dimensional hyperbolic space.

